ld when I saw them using the Clover brewing system.That said, it was hot, and I needed something cool.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '52-revision-4', '', '', '2010-11-14 17:42:04', '2010-11-14 17:42:04', '', 52, 'http://coffeebot.co/?p=250', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
