(479, 1, '2011-01-09 16:34:39', '2011-01-09 16:34:39', 'I recently discovered Google''s Ngram Viewer and found it really fascinating. For those of you who haven''t experienced the sheer excitement of this sort of thing, I''ll briefly explain: Google has digitized millions of books and made every word of them search-able, so when you type in a certain word, you can see how often that word has shown up in literature through the course of history. Of course, after punching in all the usual suspects: war, peace; male, female; Coke, Pepsi; I punched in coffee and tea. The graph acted a little like I thought it might with tea being fairly dominant for most of history. Both examples rise with the spread of literature and books for the people, but I noticed the rise and fall of these words seem to coincide with fairly big historical events. Anyone remember the Boston Tea Party? I am curious then, what other big coffee and tea historical events might be reflected on the graph? For those of you who are A) more knowledgeable of history than I am, and B) more knowledgeable of coffee than I am, I''d love to read what you think. And hop over to Google''s Ngram site, it''s a lot of fun!\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_472" align="alignleft" width="300" caption="Coffee and Tea Ngram from 1600 to now"]<a href="http://coffeebot.co/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/ngram-1600-now.jpg"><img src="http://coffeebot.co/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/ngram-1600-now-300x190.jpg" alt="Ngram from 1600 to now" title="ngram-1600-now" width="300" height="190" class="size-medium wp-image-472" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_476" align="alignleft" width="300" caption="Ngram of Coffee & Tea in the 20th century"]<a href="http://coffeebot.co/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/ngram-20th-century1.jpg"><img src="http://coffeebot.co/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/ngram-20th-century1-300x190.jpg" alt="Ngram 20th century" title="ngram-20th-century" width="300" height="190" class="size-medium wp-image-476" /></a>[/caption]\r\n', 'Coffee & Tea, War & Peace', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '471-revision-5', '', '', '2011-01-09 16:34:39', '2011-01-09 16:34:39', '', 471, 'http://coffeebot.co/coffee-shop-reviews/471-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
