o share a table with someone if you absolutely need an outlet though, since there isn''t a huge selection of tables along the windows. \r\n\r\n<span class="first-words">The End.</span> With daily specials, coffee by the press, happy hour, decent prices (even if they are a bit odd), perks if you donate to a charity and Saturday Bluegrass concerts, Paul''s definitely gives you plenty of reasons to return and get in touch with your country-coffee side. <span class="end-icon">END</span>\r\n[mappress mapid="11"]\r\n<br />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[ad#Google Adsense Post Ad]</p>\r\n<h2>Have you been to Paul''s Coffee & Tea? Share your experience in a comment below!</h2>', 'Paul''s Coffe & Tea', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '481-revision-27', '', '', '2011-01-28 18:55:10', '2011-01-28 18:55:10', '', 481, 'http://coffeebot.co/coffee-shop-reviews/481-revision-27/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
